{"tid":1022410,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有部無線播過既卡通想搵翻","createTime":"2019-02-15T04:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T06:38:22.000Z","uid":162096,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"386e121175c26fcc3b7f918abbb1bdbd5ac3aa70","tid":1022410,"uid":162096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:08:38.000Z","msg":"突然有套日本動畫想搵翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記得係細個既時候係無線睇到<br />\n肯定係2009年之前 應該1999年之後<br />\n腦入面淨係記得一幕係成班女人好似分哂等級/名次<br />\n係到賽跑 每人都推住舉重果啲鐵餅係度跑 <br />\n應該係有小小科幻唔係最現代果啲場景<br />\n好似有幾集都係講緊佢地鬥快<br />\n<br />\n當時唔記得要做咩睇左幾集冇得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但果時覺得幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知全能連登仔可唔可以KO我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f11bc2ec0e0aa279e8f6684f43c2a721781db96","tid":1022410,"uid":7314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:10:39.000Z","msg":"美少女戰士"},{"pid":"2e3f2aaf337c0fbe1ca98e5bef4d0fd6fb279987","tid":1022410,"uid":105446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:10:49.000Z","msg":"超時空金牌小女將/大運動會"},{"pid":"bca2404d628825ae568630d7f0de208a6c6f9c65","tid":1022410,"uid":171233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:11:43.000Z","msg":"最尾個集係咪食東甩"},{"pid":"09c17a950a13abb65d9b6f58d53487ebc075adf2","tid":1022410,"uid":59887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:13:55.000Z","msg":"後段同外星人比賽<br />\n最尾同佢老母鬥跑<br />\n首歌唐韋琪姐姐唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd13ca3d08df933dd2c158b99e9898a53b11fc2","tid":1022410,"uid":162096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f11bc2ec0e0aa279e8f6684f43c2a721781db96","tid":1022410,"uid":7314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:10:39.000Z","msg":"美少女戰士"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:15:54.000Z","msg":"<im